OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be dry with
OL,6,Fplenty of sunshine, some patchy cloud
OL,7,Fin the southeast at first. Remaining
OL,8,Fdry and sunny this afternoon but some
OL,9,Fhigh cloud spilling north. Brisk
OL,10,Feasterly winds along the east coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry this evening with some
OL,13,Flate brightness. Then the rest of the
OL,14,Fnight will remain dry with some high
OL,15,Fcloud around. Brisk easterly winds
OL,16,Falong the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
