OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,6,Fday with plenty of sunshine although
OL,7,Fsome high cloud around. Feeling warm
OL,8,Fin the sunshine although cooler along
OL,9,Fthe east coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,12,Fdry and settled into the weekend with
OL,13,Fsome warm sunshine. Perhaps turning
OL,14,Fcloudier on Sunday.
